  "design_notes": "The chart escalates perfectly to match the song's energy curve. The intro uses a clean 8th-note baseline with sporadic syncopated 16th-note decorations. The drops feature highly technical rhythmic hold segments, which represent the heavy synth leads, while the drop peak escalates into continuous 16th-note rolls to test the player's stamina and agility. Gaps and breather sections are naturally placed to allow physical recovery and maintain under the sustained 8.0 NPS budget.",
